title: 4K・ 【4K】Kanamara matsuri - penis festival
description:
Not a vlog, no intrusive faces or talking, pure Japan only.
This festival is dedicated to curing venereal diseases held every first Sunday of April at Kanayama shrine.
Shrine location https://goo.gl/maps/Pk4DvFU9XR12
